title: What the New Hampshire results mean for Democratic contenders
text: Breaking down New Hampshire primary results Senator Bernie Sanders came out on top in the New Hampshire primary, but former mayor Pete Buttigieg and Senator Amy Klobuchar weren't far behind. CBS News political correspondent Ed O'Keefe joined CBSN AM with more on what these results mean as the race to the White House heats up.
